{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "bca082b7-aa32-4631-b371-962c6965d55c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/bca082b7-aa32-4631-b371-962c6965d55c@1.pkg/1772597659890/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597660868", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/bca082b7-aa32-4631-b371-962c6965d55c@1.pkg/1772597659890/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597660868"}, "identifier": "bca082b7-aa32-4631-b371-962c6965d55c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查法律对社会发展的作用</p>\n\n<p>A：错误，学校对小林破坏公物进行批评教育，这是学校的管理行为，属于纪律约束，并非法律层面的规范，不能体现法律促进社会发展。​</p>\n\n<p>B：正确，小赵欠债不还，法院依法判决其履行还款义务，这体现了法律通过解决民事纠纷，维护社会公平正义和经济秩序，从而促进社会的健康发展，符合题意。​</p>\n\n<p>C：错误，小陈年满 16 岁可以自主打零工，这是法律对公民劳动权利的年龄规定，更多体现的是法律保障公民权利，而非直接促进社会发展。​</p>\n\n<p>D：错误，小孙参与小区环保活动是自愿的社会公益行为，属于道德层面的自觉，与法律无关，不能体现法律的作用。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）下列行为直接体现出法律能促进社会发展的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（原创）下列行为直接体现出法律能促进社会发展的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/bca082b7-aa32-4631-b371-962c6965d55c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143705643", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": f